      "content": "wait u said bronchodilator... i dont have a prescription for one. if i just take a heavy dose of cetirizine (zyrtec) will that help clear the wheezing since the pollen is probably what triggered it? i really dont want to go to the doc if i can help it, it's just hay fever right?",
